ersities and colleges in Turkey]]\n[[Category:State universities and colleges in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Buildings and structures in Ad\u0131yaman Province]]\n[[Category:2006 establishments in Turkey]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox university\n|image_name= \n|image_size= \n|name      = Ad\u0131yaman University\n|native_name= Ad\u0131yaman \u00dcniversitesi\n|established= 2006\n|type= [[Public university|Public]]\n|rector= Mustafa Talha GONULLU \n|staff= \n|faculty= \n|students= \n|\n|city      = [[Ad\u0131yaman]] \n|country    = [[Turkey]] \n|website    = [http://www.adiyaman.edu.tr adiyaman.edu.tr]\n}}\n\n'''Ad\u0131yaman University''' is a state university, established in 2006 in [[Ad\u0131yaman]] province, Turkey.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.adiyaman.edu.tr/index.php?lo%3Dhakkinda |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2010-11-19 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101120052512/http://adiyaman.edu.tr/index.php?lo=hakkinda |archivedate=2010-11-20 }}</ref>\n\n== Departments ==\n*Faculty of Engineering\n*Faculty of [https://web.archive.org/web/20101030230846/http://www.adiyaman.edu.tr/akabirim/iibf/ Economics and Managerial Sciences]\n*Faculty of [https://web.archive.org/web/20110423110146/http://www.adiyaman.edu.tr/akabirim/fef/ Science and Letters]\n*Faculty of [https://web.archive.org/web/20100501162303/http://www.adiyaman.edu.tr/akabirim/teknoloji/ Technology]\n*Faculty of [https://web.archive.org/web/20110220181134/http://www.adiyaman.edu.tr/akabirim/tip/ Medicine]\n*Faculty of [https://web.archive.org/web/20110423110122/http://www.adiyaman.edu.tr/akabirim/egitim/ Educational Sciences]\n*Besni Vocational High School\n*G\u00f6lba\u015f\u0131 Vocational High School\n*Kahta Vocational High School\n*Ad\u0131yaman Vocational High School\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.adiyaman.edu.tr Ad\u0131yaman University website]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Universities in Turkey}}\n\n{{coord|37|44|38|N|38|13|54|E|region:TR-02_type:edu_source:kolossus-de